scripts.backend-build: tsc -p src/backend && webpack --config backend-webpack.config.js && webpack --config serverAdmin-webpack.config.js && webpack --config adminServer-webpack.config.js && npm run build-after-copy-contrib && npm run build-after-copy-contrib-solrlang && npm run build-after-copy-overrides-config
scripts.backend-build-stats: tsc -p src/backend && webpack --config backend-webpack.config.js --profile --json > dist/server-stats.json && webpack --config serverAdmin-webpack.config.js  --profile --json > dist/serveradmin-stats.json && webpack --config adminServer-webpack.config.js  --profile --json > dist/adminserver-stats.json && npm run build-after-copy-contrib && npm run build-after-copy-contrib-solrlang && npm run build-after-copy-overrides-config
scripts.backend-build-and-serve-dev: npm run backend-build && npm run backend-serve-dev
scripts.backend-test: tsc -p src/backend/tsconfig.spec.json && istanbul cover node_modules/jasmine/bin/jasmine.js -- --config=backend.jasmine.json && remap-istanbul -i ./coverage/backend-js/coverage.json -t html -o ./coverage/backend
scripts.build-dev: npm run build-before-prepare && npm run build-dev-de && npm run build-dev-en && npm run build-after-copy-overrides-dist-dev
scripts.build-dev-de-stats: ng build frontend --base-href=/myshpdev/de/ --configuration=dev-de --aot true --stats-json true --output-path dist/static/myshpdev/de
scripts.build-beta: npm run build-before-prepare && npm run build-beta-de && npm run build-beta-en && npm run build-after-copy-overrides-dist-beta
scripts.build-prod: npm run build-before-prepare && npm run build-prod-de && npm run build-prod-en && npm run build-after-copy-overrides-dist-prod
scripts.build-viewer: npm run build-before-prepare && npm run build-viewer-de && npm run build-viewer-en && npm run build-after-copy-overrides-dist-viewer
scripts.build-viewer-de: ng build frontend --configuration=viewer-de --aot true --output-path dist/static/myshpviewer/de && npm run build-after-copy-preinline-de && cross-var node devtools/create-allinone-html.js dist/static/myshpviewer/de/index.viewer.html dist/static/myshpviewer/de/index.viewer.full.html "" noexclusions $npm_package_config_viewerpassword
scripts.build-viewer-en: ng build frontend --configuration=viewer-en --aot true --output-path dist/static/myshpviewer/en && npm run build-after-copy-preinline-en && cross-var node devtools/create-allinone-html.js dist/static/myshpviewer/en/index.viewer.html dist/static/myshpviewer/en/index.viewer.full.html "" noexclusions $npm_package_config_viewerpassword
scripts.build-viewer-de-stats: ng build frontend --configuration=viewer-de --aot true --stats-json true --output-path dist/static/myshpviewer/de && npm run build-after-copy-preinline-de && node devtools/create-allinone-html.js dist/static/myshpviewer/de/index.viewer.html dist/static/myshpviewer/de/index.viewer.full.html
scripts.build-after-copy-preinline-de: cpx --include-empty-dirs --verbose "node_modules/lz-string/libs/lz-string.min.js" dist/static/myshpviewer/de/ && cpx --include-empty-dirs --verbose "devtools/webloader.js" dist/static/myshpviewer/de/ && cpx --include-empty-dirs --verbose "overrides/after-build/dist/myshpviewer/de/**/*.* " dist/static/myshpviewer/de/
scripts.build-after-copy-preinline-en: cpx --include-empty-dirs --verbose "node_modules/lz-string/libs/lz-string.min.js" dist/static/myshpviewer/en/ && cpx --include-empty-dirs --verbose "devtools/webloader.js" dist/static/myshpviewer/en/ && cpx --include-empty-dirs --verbose "overrides/after-build/dist/myshpviewer/en/**/*.* " dist/static/myshpviewer/en/
scripts.frontendserver-build-and-serve-dev-de: npm run frontendserver-build-dev-de && npm run frontendserver-build-server-dev-de && npm run frontendserver-serve-dev-de
scripts.frontendserver-build-and-serve-beta-de: npm run frontendserver-build-beta-de && npm run frontendserver-build-server-beta-de && npm run frontendserver-serve-beta-de
scripts.frontendserver-build-and-serve-prod-de: npm run frontendserver-build-prod-de && npm run frontendserver-build-server-prod-de && npm run frontendserver-serve-prod-de
scripts.generate-sitemaps-dev: node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --command generateSitemap --action generateSitemap --adminclibackend config/adminCli.dev.json --backend config/backend.dev.json config/sitemap-de.json && node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --command generateSitemap --action generateSitemap --adminclibackend config/adminCli.dev.json --backend config/backend.dev.json config/sitemap-en.json
scripts.generate-sitemaps-beta: node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --command generateSitemap --action generateSitemap --adminclibackend config/adminCli.beta.json --backend config/backend.beta.json config/sitemap-de.json && node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --command generateSitemap --action generateSitemap --adminclibackend config/adminCli.beta.json --backend config/backend.beta.json config/sitemap-en.json
scripts.generate-sitemaps-prod: node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --command generateSitemap --action generateSitemap --adminclibackend config/adminCli.prod.json --backend config/backend.prod.json config/sitemap-de.json && node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --command generateSitemap --action generateSitemap --adminclibackend config/adminCli.prod.json --backend config/backend.prod.json config/sitemap-en.json
scripts.init-cache-dev: node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --adminclibackend config/adminCli.dev.json --backend config/backend.dev.json --command initCache --action initCache
scripts.init-cache-beta: node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --adminclibackend config/adminCli.beta.json --backend config/backend.beta.json --command initCache --action initCache
scripts.init-cache-prod: node dist/backend/serverAdmin.js --adminclibackend config/adminCli.prod.json --backend config/backend.prod.json --command initCache --action initCache
scripts.install-solr-doit: npm run install-solr-clear && npm run install-solr-download && npm run install-solr-unpack && npm run install-solr-cleanout && npm run install-solr-download-langfiles && npm run install-solr-convert-langfiles && npm run install-solr-download-dataimport

install-solr-clear-os.win32: node_modules\.bin\rimraf contrib/solr && node_modules\.bin\mkdirp contrib/solr && node_modules\.bin\mkdirp contrib/solr/contrib/dataimporthandler/lib && node_modules\.bin\mkdirp contrib/solr/contrib/lang

scripts.install-solr-download-langfiles: cd contrib && curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/elastic/hunspell/master/dicts/de_DE/de_DE.dic -o solr/contrib/lang/hunspell_de_DE.dic && curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/elastic/hunspell/master/dicts/de_DE/de_DE.aff -o solr/contrib/lang/hunspell_de_DE.aff && curl https://netix.dl.sourceforge.net/project/germandict/german.7z -o solr/contrib/lang/german.7z
scripts.install-solr-download-dataimport: npm run install-solr-download-dataimport-mysql && npm run install-solr-download-dataimport-sqlite
scripts.install-solr-unpack: cd contrib && tar xzf solr.tgz -C solr --strip-components=1
scripts.prepare: patch-package && npm run prepare-symlinks && npm run prepare-build && npm run prepare-build-before-copy-overrides-installer && npm run prepare-build-before-copy-overrides-sbin && npm run prepare-build-before-copy-overrides-src && npm run prepare-build-before-copy-overrides-devtools
scripts.prepare-symlinks: symlink-dir src/shared src/backend/shared && symlink-dir src/shared src/frontend/shared && symlink-dir src/shared src/frontendserver/shared

prepare-build-os.win32: node_modules\.bin\rimraf node_modules\@dps\*\node_modules\@dps & node_modules\.bin\rimraf dist && node_modules\.bin\mkdirp dist && node_modules\.bin\mkdirp src\shared

scripts.start: npm run build-before-prepare && ng serve frontend --watch --aot true --configuration de --proxy-config proxy.conf.json
scripts.start-en: npm run build-before-prepare && ng serve frontend --watch --aot true --configuration en --proxy-config proxy.conf.json
scripts.test: npm run build-before-prepare && ng test frontend --preserveSymlinks=true --environment=dev --watch=false
scripts.testCoverage: npm run build-before-prepare && ng test frontend --preserveSymlinks=true --environment=dev --code-coverage true --watch=false
scripts.testwatch: npm run build-before-prepare && ng test frontend --preserveSymlinks=true --environment=dev --watch=true
scripts.xi18n: ng xi18n frontend --locale de --out-file messages.de.xlf --output-path src/frontend/locales/ --i18n-format xlf --verbose --progress
scripts.xi18n-en: ng xi18n frontend --locale en --out-file messages.en.xlf --output-path src/frontend/locales/ --i18n-format xlf --verbose --progress

dependencyHints.@babel/runtime-corejs3: fixed to prevent 'TypeError: l is undefined' on viewer and builded versions
dependencyHints.core-js-pure: fixed to prevent 'TypeError: l is undefined' on viewer and builded versions
